775
00:46:31,997 --> 00:46:32,915
This is my problem.

776
00:46:33,916 --> 00:46:35,626
He might end up abandoning you.

777
00:46:35,709 --> 00:46:37,920
I'm the one who chose him.

778
00:46:38,003 --> 00:46:40,255
