00:47:23,882 --> 00:47:25,425
It's already pretty late.

789
00:47:25,509 --> 00:47:27,010
Let's go back to the National Assembly

790
00:47:27,094 --> 00:47:28,303
and decide what to do.

791
00:47:46,280 --> 00:47:48,198
Mr. Jo was really out of line.

792
00:47:48,282 --> 00:47:49,533
We work for the same party.

793
00:47:49,616 --> 00:47:50,951
Isn't it obvious what he's doing?

794
00:47:51,034 --> 00:47:53,912
