or something?

795
00:47:53,996 --> 00:47:56,498
We won't be able to do anything
during the inspection like this.

796
00:47:56,582 --> 00:47:58,709
-When will the hearing resume?
-In an hour.

797
00:47:59,042 --> 00:48:00,127
Hand me the list of questions.

798
00:48:00,210 --> 00:48:02,254
-The list.
-Yes, here it is.

799
00:48:13,098 --> 00:48:15,559
-You're aware of Bugang--
