800
00:48:15,642 --> 00:48:18,770
Most of the subcontractors
currently working at Bugang Electronics

801
00:48:18,896 --> 00:48:21,732
-I said, no off-topic questions.
-insist that dangerous tasks

802
00:48:21,815 --> 00:48:23,901
-are generally given to subcontractors--
-Time's up.

803
00:48:26,987 --> 00:48:28,947
Could you look into firms
that have ties to Bugang?

804
00:48:29,031 --> 00:48:29,907
Of course.

805
00:48:29,990 --> 00:48:30,991
Let's go.

806
00:48:35,829 --> 00:48:39,791
