to bog us down using Lee Chang-jin.

807
00:48:39,875 --> 00:48:41,376
If it doesn't resume today,

808
00:48:41,460 --> 00:48:43,962
it'll be hard to bring in
the CEO of Bugang as a witness again.

809
00:48:44,046 --> 00:48:45,923
I'm aware, but we can't do anything

810
00:48:46,006 --> 00:48:48,634
until the game begins.

811
00:48:49,301 --> 00:48:51,637
God, this is incredibly frustrating.

812
00:48:51,720 --> 00:48:54,973
Hello, I devoted 30 years of my life

813
00:48:55,057 --> 00:48:58,894
-to Bugang Electronics.
-Jeez, those morons protest all the time.

814
00:48:59,561 --> 00:49:00,729
Any ideas?

815
00:49:05,776 --> 00:49:06,902
Mr. Lee.

816
00:49:06,985 --> 00:49:08,070
Yes, Ms. Kang.

817
00:49:12,658 --> 00:49:13,492
What is this?

818
00:49:22,334 --> 00:49:24,836
